[%#
  MarkerLegend.tt — compact one-line hint with tooltips. Include directly before each multi-value field in edit mode.
%]<div style="font-size:0.82em;color:#555;margin:0 0 2px;"><strong title="Separate multiple terms with a semicolon (;) — each term is individually linked and validated on save">Semicolons:</strong> <code><span title="A plain term — linked to the matching Glossary, Therapeutic Action, Constituent, or other ENCY record on save">demulcent; diuretic;</span> <span title="Append [?] to flag this term for RESEARCH — a todo is created automatically on save reminding you to verify and source this term" style="color:#856404;">adaptogen[?];</span> <span title="Append [ref?] to flag this term for REFERENCE VERIFICATION — a todo is created on save reminding you to find and add an authoritative citation for this term" style="color:#856404;">demulcent[ref?]</span></code></div>
